text: Lycomimus formosus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Chemsak and Linsley in 1984. It is known from Panama.BioLib.cz - Lycomimus formosus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1984
